Book.create(title: "Witness for the Prosecution", author: "Agatha Christie", img_url: "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ri-yyUadvWAC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api", description: "Thriller / Characters: 8 male, 5 female Scenery: 2 Interiors Only Agatha Christie could have conceived such a suspenseful thriller and then capped it with an uncanny triple flip ending.")
